ote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n點會唔知</blockquote><br />\n講黎聽下</blockquote><br />\n航班延誤</blockquote><br />\n跨時區旅行或洽公對現代人來說是司空見慣的事，但在長時飛行結束時，人們可能或多或少會出現所謂<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時差</span></span>（Jet lag）症狀，如白天過度嗜睡、睡眠障礙等，症狀嚴重程度也與個人敏感性有所差異，時差對於旅人來說是一件困擾的事。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE :<a href=\"http://www.taic.mohw.gov.tw/?aid=509&amp;pid=88&amp;page_name=detail&amp;type=1143&amp;iid=1854\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.taic.mohw.gov.tw%2F%3Faid%3D509%26pid%3D88%26page_name%3Ddetail%26type%3D1143%26iid%3D1854&d=i9CbHxcJtuCueviEpLrmVQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=55727bd7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.taic.mohw.gov.tw/?aid=509&amp;pid=88&amp;page_name=detail&amp;type=1143&amp;iid=1854</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣香港都係GMT+8 何來時差之有?</blockquote><br />\n咁我依加周身唔舒服唔撚係JET LAG可以係咩</blockquote><br />\n你自己有病囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c58198af7aca63a830524c83ecc0793e447ffc5","tid":358870,"uid":81756,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T04:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你知唔知jet lag點解</blockquote><br />\n點會唔知</blockquote><br />\n講黎聽下</blockquote><br />\n航班延誤</blockquote><br />\n跨時區旅行或洽公對現代人來說是司空見慣的事，但在長時飛行結束時，人們可能或多或少會出現所謂<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時差</span></span>（Jet lag）症狀，如白天過度嗜睡、睡眠障礙等，症狀嚴重程度也與個人敏感性有所差異，時差對於旅人來說是一件困擾的事。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE :<a href=\"http://www.taic.mohw.gov.tw/?aid=509&amp;pid=88&amp;page_name=detail&amp;type=1143&amp;iid=1854\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.taic.mohw.gov.tw%2F%3Faid%3D509%26pid%3D88%26page_name%3Ddetail%26type%3D1143%26iid%3D1854&d=i9CbHxcJtuCueviEpLrmVQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=55727bd7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.taic.mohw.gov.tw/?aid=509&amp;pid=88&amp;page_name=detail&amp;type=1143&amp;iid=1854</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣